<br/>
a is an integer ranging from 0 to 20.
</p>
<p id="p-0023" num="0022">Another aspect of the present invention is a process for conditioning hair and skin which comprises contacting the hair or skin with an effective conditioning concentration of a polyester that conforms to the following structure:</p>
<p id="p-0024" num="0023"><chemistry id="CHEM-US-00004" num="00004">
