</p>
<p id="p-0029" num="0028">(b) HO&#x2014;(CH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>3</sub>&#x2014;OH, a natural diol made from corn;</p>
<p id="p-0030" num="0029">(c) a fatty alcohol conforming to the following structure:
<br/>
