</p>
<p id="p-0031" num="0030">b is an integer ranging from 6 to 31 or mixtures thereof.</p>
<p id="p-0032" num="0031">Another aspect of the present invention is a process for conditioning hair and skin which comprises contacting the hair or skin with an effective conditioning concentration of a polyester made by the esterification reaction of:</p>
<p id="h-0008" num="0000">(a) citric acid conforming to the following structure:</p>
<p id="p-0033" num="0032"><chemistry id="CHEM-US-00006" num="00006">
